sequenceDiagram
  participant C as Client
  participant F as Security Filter
  participant T as Token Service
  participant S as Spring Security
  participant DB as Database

  C->>F: Request + Authorization header
  F->>F: Extract Bearer token
  F->>T: validateToken(jwt)
  T->>T: Verify HMAC256 signature + expiry
  T-->>F: User email
  F->>DB: Find user by email
  DB-->>F: User entity
  F->>S: Set authentication context
  S-->>C: Request proceeds to controller
